description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Warm Up Cycling Workout' from the channel Kaleigh Cohen Cycling.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Groove Session vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This warm up ride is for ANY cycling or strength workout to get your body ready to KICK BUTT!! 


If you're a beginner and working to build up to a 20 minute cycling workout, this rhythm ride is what you need! 

I'm so glad you decided to join my cycling class today, let's go for a ride! Grab your water bottle, grab your towel, get on your bike and let's get these pedals spinning! - Kaleigh Cohen Fitness
